law.history: Repealed 1972 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 3, sec. 93, effective January 1, 1973. -- Created 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 270, sec. 5.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Disposition of funds derived from fees and forfeiture of bonds; lapse of trust and agency accounts; fund for financing grant-in-aid projects.
